7// copyvertex.h: Defines vertex buffer copying and conversion functions
8
9#ifndef LIBANGLE_RENDERER_COPYVERTEX_H_
10#define LIBANGLE_RENDERER_COPYVERTEX_H_
11
12#include "common/mathutil.h"
13
14namespace rx
15{
16
17using VertexCopyFunction = void (*)(const uint8_t *input,
18 size_t stride,
19 size_t count,
20 uint8_t *output);
21
22// 'alphaDefaultValueBits' gives the default value for the alpha channel (4th component)
23template <typename T,
24 size_t inputComponentCount,
25 size_t outputComponentCount,
26 uint32_t alphaDefaultValueBits>
27void CopyNativeVertexData(const uint8_t *input, size_t stride, size_t count, uint8_t *output);
28
29template <size_t inputComponentCount, size_t outputComponentCount>
30void Copy8SintTo16SintVertexData(const uint8_t *input,
31 size_t stride,
32 size_t count,
33 uint8_t *output);
34
35template <size_t componentCount>
36void Copy8SnormTo16SnormVertexData(const uint8_t *input,
37 size_t stride,
38 size_t count,
39 uint8_t *output);
40
41template <size_t inputComponentCount, size_t outputComponentCount>
42void Copy32FixedTo32FVertexData(const uint8_t *input, size_t stride, size_t count, uint8_t *output);
43
44template <typename T, size_t inputComponentCount, size_t outputComponentCount, bool normalized>
45void CopyTo32FVertexData(const uint8_t *input, size_t stride, size_t count, uint8_t *output);
46
47template <size_t inputComponentCount, size_t outputComponentCount>
48void Copy32FTo16FVertexData(const uint8_t *input, size_t stride, size_t count, uint8_t *output);
49
50void CopyXYZ32FToXYZ9E5(const uint8_t *input, size_t stride, size_t count, uint8_t *output);
51
52void CopyXYZ32FToX11Y11B10F(const uint8_t *input, size_t stride, size_t count, uint8_t *output);
53
54template <bool isSigned, bool normalized, bool toFloat>
55void CopyXYZ10W2ToXYZW32FVertexData(const uint8_t *input,
56 size_t stride,
57 size_t count,
58 uint8_t *output);
59
60template <bool isSigned, bool normalized>
61void CopyXYZ10ToXYZW32FVertexData(const uint8_t *input,
62 size_t stride,
63 size_t count,
64 uint8_t *output);
65
66template <bool isSigned, bool normalized>
67void CopyW2XYZ10ToXYZW32FVertexData(const uint8_t *input,
68 size_t stride,
69 size_t count,
70 uint8_t *output);
71
72} // namespace rx
73
74#include "copyvertex.inc.h"
75
76#endif // LIBANGLE_RENDERER_COPYVERTEX_H_
